<br>
Look at the changes to melees. Melee rebalancing was &quot;done&quot; about a year ago. Now we see monk defensive power go down, while rangers receive a BIG defense upgrade. Warriors and some other classes also received upgrades to their dodge skill.<br>
<br>
Now I wont argue that anything of what they did is bad, but it seems obvious that there is some TOTALLY different view of how the classes should be balanced to each other than a while ago. I really would like to have VI communicate a bit more of how they see classes in balance to each other, especially if you consider that melee balancing was considered over quite a while ago, and caster balancing is still in progress.<br>
<br>
Of course changes to the game can make things unbalanced, but I would still like them to tell us why they think something has to be changed. I can understand the monk change, and the warrior change, but the ranger upgrade??<br>
<br>
